00:00:26.792 --> 00:00:29.796 align:start position:0%
where employees
can wear jeans once a month.

00:00:29.829 --> 00:00:32.832
- Well, that was
a catastrophic mistake.

00:00:32.865 --> 00:00:34.934
Just look at that.

00:00:34.967 --> 00:00:37.837
I mean, how can someone
lack the shame and dignity

00:00:37.870 --> 00:00:39.839
to come into an office
looking like that?

