with those toes?

00:00:52.318 --> 00:00:54.754 line:0%
The second one is too long.
It should be covered.

00:00:54.787 --> 00:00:56.823
Why would he subject us to this?

00:00:56.856 --> 00:00:58.491
I don't want to see
another human being's foot

00:00:58.524 --> 00:01:00.226
for the rest of the day.

00:01:00.259 --> 00:01:04.397
- Wow. This is definitely gonna
be a traumatic memory for me.

00:01:04.430 --> 00:01:07.100
- Alyssa Armstrong is going to
be here within the hour,

00:01:07.133 --> 00:01:10.369
and she represents
Glorious Salvation Ministries,

00:01:10.402 --> 00:01:13.606
the largest group
of mega-churches in the country,

00:01:13.639 --> 00:01:15.608
