00:01:22.748 --> 00:01:23.950 align:start position:0%
- [sobs]

00:01:23.983 --> 00:01:27.887
- Now, we all know
there's no God,

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:30.723
but there is...

00:01:30.756 --> 00:01:34.193
a ton of money
to be made in his name.

00:01:34.226 --> 00:01:36.863
So let's try to act
like professionals today.

00:01:36.896 --> 00:01:39.465 align:start position:0%
- [weeping]

00:01:39.498 --> 00:01:41.434
